  "text": "The studied population presented a mean age of [CITATION_1] Table 1 . In accordance with periodontal parameters for cytokine analysis and DC evaluation, individuals were classified as presenting either mild-moderate CP (n = 10) or advanced CP (n = 14 for cytokines; n = 12 for DCs).",
